        <mxCell id="t-item" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:13px;color:#E65100&quot;&gt;Product Items&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr size=&quot;1&quot;&gt;🔑 ID — NVARCHAR(36) — PK&lt;br&gt;serial_number — NVARCHAR(40) — Unique per batch&lt;br&gt;upi — NVARCHAR(60) — Unique global&lt;br&gt;item_status — NVARCHAR(12) — enum, Default active&lt;br&gt;created_date — DATE&lt;br&gt;🔗 batch_ID — NVARCHAR(36) — FK, Required&lt;br&gt;🔗 dpp_ID — NVARCHAR(36) — FK" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#F57C00;fontColor=#E65100;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;spacingRight=10;strokeWidth=2;" vertex="1" parent="1">
