        <mxCell id="t-bom" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:13px;color:#E65100&quot;&gt;Product BOMs&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr size=&quot;1&quot;&gt;🔑 ID — NVARCHAR(36) — PK&lt;br&gt;quantity — DECIMAL(10, 3)&lt;br&gt;unit — NVARCHAR(8)&lt;br&gt;component_role — NVARCHAR(60)&lt;br&gt;is_mandatory — BOOLEAN — Default true&lt;br&gt;status — NVARCHAR(12) — enum, Default active&lt;br&gt;🔗 parent_ID — NVARCHAR(36) — FK to Products, Required&lt;br&gt;🔗 component_ID — NVARCHAR(36) — FK to Products, Required&lt;br&gt;🔗 linked_dpp_ID — NVARCHAR(36) — FK to DPPs (optional)&lt;hr size=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;i style=&quot;font-size:9px&quot;&gt;Constraint: unique (parent_ID, component_ID)&lt;/i&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#F57C00;fontColor=#E65100;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;spacingRight=10;strokeWidth=2;" vertex="1" parent="1">
